snippet.textDisplay: Good old simple guitar lead!...2:02 gotta love it! 3:55 elctric lead is powerful too...changes the mood of the song...becomes passionate...4:21 the senior smiles at the junior! that's some compliment! Wonderful to see musicians enjoying each others as well as their own work! 3:46 time to change into electric! need more power, rt? 4:32 adding shehnai was a brilliant idea! This transports one into a higher level of rich compostition. Such a gem of a song over all. Papon has arrived in this one! His passion, emotion and involvement are outstanding. It's a rare piece of art!
